    {
      "id": "optimistic_11_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_11",
      "description": "\ud83c\udf1f Mint Condition & Absolutely Stunning \u2014 A Rare Find You Don't Want to Miss! This exceptional used car is in mint condition \u2014 and we mean it! From bumper to bumper, this vehicle looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior is virtually flawless, with no meaningful scratches, dents, or blemishes to speak of. The interior is equally impressive \u2014 fresh, clean, and beautifully preserved with no signs of significant wear. Under the hood, everything is running perfectly, and the mechanicals are in top-notch shape. If you've been searching for a used car that truly feels new, this is the one. Opportunities like this don't come around often \u2014 come see it for yourself!",
      "price": 45000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 14
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is listed at $7,500, a price that honestly reflects its poor overall condition. The exterior shows significant wear \u2014 expect multiple scratches, noticeable paint fading, and likely some dents or rust spots. Mechanically, the car has known issues and will require attention; it is drivable but should not be considered reliable without repairs. This listing is best suited for a buyer comfortable with a project vehicle, someone looking for parts, or a mechanically inclined individual who can address the needed work. A pre-purchase inspection is strongly encouraged so you know exactly what you're getting into. No major surprises are being hidden here \u2014 this is an honest price for an honestly worn car.",
      "price": 7500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 14
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is being listed honestly to reflect its true current condition \u2014 it is in poor shape and is best suited for a buyer looking for a project car, parts vehicle, or someone with strong mechanical skills and a willingness to invest time and money into restoration. The car shows significant wear both inside and out: the exterior has noticeable rust, dents, and faded paint, while the interior is worn with torn upholstery and damaged trim pieces. Mechanically, the vehicle has known issues that will require attention before it can be considered reliably road-worthy. It starts and moves under its own power, but should not be expected to perform like a daily driver without substantial work. There are no hidden surprises here \u2014 what you see is what you get. This listing is priced accordingly to reflect the car's current state, making it an honest opportunity for the right buyer who knows what they're getting into.",
      "price": 5000.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 14
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in good, well-maintained condition \u2014 a solid choice for a buyer looking for a reliable used car without paying mint-condition prices. The exterior presents nicely overall, with only minor surface blemishes, small scratches, or light wear consistent with normal everyday use; nothing that detracts significantly from its appearance. The paint retains a good shine, and the body panels are straight with no major dents or rust concerns. Inside, the cabin is clean and functional \u2014 the upholstery shows moderate wear on high-contact areas like the driver's seat and door panels, but there are no tears, stains, or damage that would raise concern. All primary controls, windows, and climate systems operate as expected. Mechanically, the vehicle runs well and has been maintained adequately; it starts reliably, drives smoothly, and handles everyday commuting and highway driving without issue. Tires have reasonable tread remaining, and brakes are in serviceable condition. This is not a showroom-perfect vehicle, but it is genuinely dependable and presents good value for the price. Buyers should expect a car that is ready to use daily with only routine maintenance needs going forward.",
      "price": 35000.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 14
    }
